    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "cool. i want the guide to be really helpful for them so they don't feel lost. maybe we can include some info on how the quality of the travel recommendations might change? i want them to know that even though the new thing is faster, the personal touch they're used to with you might be different. what do you think?",
